snippet.title: The Red Lantern Reveal
snippet.description:
The Red Lantern is a rogue-lite, narrative game where you and your team of 5 sled dogs, lost in the wilderness, must navigate the ever-changing events of the Alaskan bush to find your way home.

More details will be revealed later this year.

Website: http://timberline.studio
Twitter: @timberlinegames
